<br>
I picked some up for 1k the other day and I am really digging them.  I am still wanting the ES vambraces but this is a good upgrade from my gnomeskin gloves.  I used them to great effect hunting Wurms in BW last night, which was thier first battle test.  I would stil use ensnare in a dungon, but outdorrs, these are just great.<br>
<br>
I have just been reading about them since I bought them, and many sem to not really like them.  This combined with the unlimited root from the Tunare Necklace, ES Vambraces, and Lumi Staff would be an extremely nice set-up:)<br>
<br>
Fairweather Pure <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rtfm>rtfm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 11:54:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ES Gauntlets</span><hr size=1> You got a good deal on them.<br>
<br>
I love mine.<br>
<br>
First pair I got I traded for the arms.<br>
<br>
Then got another pair later. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usilleyeskimo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SilleyEskimo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 12:40:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ES Gauntlets</span><hr size=1> Funny you mention that...I was thinking along those same lines.<br>
<br>
Fairweather Pure <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udiscordian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>discordian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 3:44:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> want mine?</span><hr size=1> I never use mine, I'm trying to unload them.  Ensnare's duration makes it far superior outdoors, and since if I'm in a dungeon, I'm grouped, and if I'm grouped, there is usually a high level ranger or necro with me, I rarely end up snaring.<br>
<br>
If they had Ensnare, or were instant-cast, I'd love them.  But I can't justify freeing up the ensnare spell slot for the snare on the gloves.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uligge.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ligge</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 4:04:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eqguide.com/images/vermsmall.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ES Gauntlets</span><hr size=1> I used them often, dungeons too for a long while. I just recently got the Crystal (10ac 5str 35mana) ones and the ES are currently banked. <p><p><font face="Tahoma" size="1">Ligge - Fennin Ro<br><a href="http://www.eqguide.com">www.eqguide.com</a><br>
Changing Tide CoGuild Leader<br><b>
"You must be the change you wish to see in the world." - Mahatma Ghandi</b></font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufibtastormwillow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fibta Stormwillow</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 4:15:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ES guantlets</span><hr size=1> I have a pair of these.  I keep thinking that they are a good idea. But I never use em. I have coldain skin gloves and an epic. These are good intermediate level gear.<br>
<br>
I really like clickable gear.  I use ES helm, vambraces, and boots all the time.  The helm is good for camoing the group, vambraces add a dot.  The boots are great for travel.  I have hotkeys set up on my evil eye bag with gear in it and slots for boots, arms, head, hands.  I switch in and out faster than I can mem a spell.  Basically it adds some spell slots and are mana free. With the gear I mentioned above a lumi staff and a wardens necklace you would never be caught manaless.    <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukevar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kevar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 12:04:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ES Gauntlets</span><hr size=1> A guildmate gave me my pair of ES Gauntlets.  Honestly before I got them, I would have never paid for a set.  What do I need a free cast of a 20(?) mana spell?   Now that I've had them a month, I love them.   I remember complaining a few nights before I got them what I would do for 1 extra  spell slot.  These gloves give that to me.  I still prefer the faster cast and duration of ensnare, but when I really need that extra spell slot (ie, I need to keep Fury of Air or Whirling Wind memmed) I use the right click effect. <br>
<br>
Actually a few nights ago, another guildmate picked up the ES Helm and Gauntlets for 500 plat for his druid gimp.  Yikes!<br>
<br>
Kevar Gladestrider<br>
Wanderer of Veeshan <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showPrevMessage?topicID=3290.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showNextMessage?topicID=3290.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3290.topic&index=6><img src=http://dev.thedruidsgrove.org/images/forum/addreplya.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=3290.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=3290.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3290.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3290.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm29">The Druids Circle<opt